Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBQMTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.commander4j.db.JDBQMTest
  • public class JDBQMTest
extends java.lang.Object
    The JDBQMTest inserts/updates/deletes rows into the APP_QM_TEST table. This table defines the tests which are required for the associated Inspection / Activity.

    See Also:
    JDBQMInspection, JDBQMActivity, JDBQMDictionary, JDBQMSample
